cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CR 

This paper is about a framework for data repairing, which is a common problem in databases. Therefore, cs.DB (Databases) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also introduces a probabilistic inference approach, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses optimizations for scaling the approach, which is related to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
